CSS GRID - done and understand




CSS RESPONSIVE
**************
- https://www.w3schools.com/css/tryit.asp?filename=tryresponsive_col-s

CSS GRID
********
grid-area or grid template - https://www.w3schools.com/css/tryit.asp?filename=trycss_grid_layout_named

display: grid;                            - like indices
display: inline-grid;                     - 1 col na naay grid sa sulod
grid-template-columns: auto auto auto;    - 3 col with 4 col inside each
grid-template-columns: 80px 200px auto 40px;

grid-column-gap: 50px;
grid-row-gap: 50px;
grid-gap: 50px 100px;                     - gap for col and row

grid-column-start: 1;                     - unsa gilapdon ang col
grid-column-end: 3;

grid-row-start: 1;                        - unsa gilapdon ang row
grid-row-end: 3;
